        <item>
            <title>【有片睇】全程 iPhone 15 Pro Max 拍攝《28 Years Later》，預告片登場</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/11/28-years-was-shot-on-iphone-15/movie-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=28-years-was-shot-on-iphone-15</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/11/28-years-was-shot-on-iphone-15/movie-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 07:00:03 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影視娛樂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[28 Days Later]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iPhone 15 Pro Max]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1280230</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
<p>電影《28 Years Later》稍早前發布首部預告片，電影標榜全程使用 iPhone 15 Pro Max 拍攝，展示智能手機在專業電影製作領域的潛力。電影將於 2025 年 6 月 20 日在美國上映，為觀眾帶來耳目一新的驚嚇體驗。</p><p><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="28 YEARS LATER – Official Trailer (HD)" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mcvLKldPM08?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></p><p>《28 Years Later》是 2002 年上映的經典英國災難片《28 Days Later》之續集，據外媒報道，《28 Years Later》整部電影全程以 iPhone 15 Pro Max 拍攝，為影片增添了獨特的視覺風格。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280445" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/bgus_2970142_012-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/bgus_2970142_012-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/bgus_2970142_012.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Jodie Comer 在《28 Years Later》片場，外媒指右邊的攝錄系統為 iPhone 15 Pro Max<br />圖片來源：<a href="https://www.wired.com/story/28-years-later-danny-boyles-new-zombie-flick-was-shot-on-an-iphone-15/">Wired</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280444" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/6beastgripdofadapter-531x580.jpeg" alt="" width="531" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/6beastgripdofadapter-531x580.jpeg 531w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/6beastgripdofadapter.jpeg 825w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 531px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配合外置配件可安裝鏡頭至 iPhone 上，另外亦可將 iPhone 安裝在腳架上，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.wired.com/story/28-years-later-danny-boyles-new-zombie-flick-was-shot-on-an-iphone-15/">Wired</a></p><p>故事背景設定在病毒爆發 28 年（ 10,228 日）後，社會瀕臨崩潰，秩序蕩然無存。倖存者於孤島尋找避難之所，然而危機四伏，生機渺茫。導演 Danny Boyle 再度執導，演員陣容包括 Jodie Comer、 Aaron Taylor-Johnson 和 Ralph Fiennes。此外，有傳聞 Cillian Murphy 可能以喪屍形象回歸，惟未獲官方確認。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280446" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/28yearslaterofficial-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/28yearslaterofficial-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/28yearslaterofficial.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有傳，淨係睇咗 Trailier 已經覺得好期待，其中一幕有隻喪屍個輪廓有啲似 Cillian Murphy，唔知係咪真係佢嚟😏😏 將以喪屍形象回歸，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mcvLKldPM08">Sony Pictures Entertainment</a></p><p>嚴格來説，《28 Years Later》並非首部使用 iPhone 拍攝的電影，早在 2015 年 Sean Baker 已開始使用 iPhone 5S 拍攝《Tangerine》，其後 Steven Soderbergh 亦在 2018 年使用 iPhone 7Plus 拍攝《Unsane》，惟上面的電影均是限量發行的低成本藝術電影。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280447" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/tangerinesquare-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/tangerinesquare-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/tangerinesquare.jpeg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Sean Baker 在 2015 年使用 iPhone 5S 拍攝《Tangerine》，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.editmate.com/tangerine/">EditMate</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280448" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/64pjkdi5u5juevkv5rmg-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/64pjkdi5u5juevkv5rmg-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/64pjkdi5u5juevkv5rmg.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Steven Soderbergh 在 2018 年使用 iPhone 7 Plus 拍攝《Unsane》，圖片來源：The National News</p><p>作為 2002 年經典恐怖片《28 Days Later》的續集，《28 Years Later》延續了前作的末日驚悚風格。預告片現已於 YouTube 發布。《28 Years Later》是新三部曲的第一部；即將上映的三部喪屍電影均由《28 Days Later》 原編劇 Alex Garland 編寫劇本。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://9to5mac.com/2024/12/10/iphone-15-28-years-later-trailer/">9to5Mac</a>、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mcvLKldPM08">Sony Picture Entertainment@YouTube</a>、<a href="https://www.bosshunting.com.au/entertainment/movies/28-years-later-trailer/">Boss Hunting</a></p><p>====== 加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事 ========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
